## Note on prior in-tree state

Found uncommitted partial changes in the working tree on entry (hunt-fx.js, hunt-turret.js, hunt-results.js) that mirrored the worker brief but had two issues: (1) used WG.HuntPlayer.runtime.player which is not exposed publicly, (2) called WG.Game.flashScreen which was not on the export list. Reset, rebuilt clean using WG.Game.getHuntRuntime().player and added flashScreen to the WG.Game export. Concern B's HUD desaturation + audio EVENT_MAP additions were entirely missing from the prior attempt and are new.
